Subject: [PATCH] ocamlobjinfo: display the runtime used by an image

ocamlobjinfo now parses both RNTM and shebang lines in order to display
the runtime being used by a bytecode executable.

(cherry picked from commit 629efbfaae3aa87745dd3b55418a1ebe6740f156)

